{{Quote|I still say it's Mara Jade. She's a master trader, and an ex-Imperial intell operative. She's got ships, resources, technical centers, and spies everywhere, and she's real. She's no imaginary fleet of ships drifting in the Sand Crab Nebula.|Han Solo, to [[Dracmus]]|<ref name="AaS">''[[Assault at Selonia]]''</ref>}}
The '''Sand Crab Nebula''' was a made-up [[Nebula/Legends|nebula]] devised by [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]].<ref name="AaS" />

{{Neb-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
[[Jason Fry]], co-author of ''[[The Essential Atlas]]'', indicated in [[June]] [[2015]] that the Sand Crab Nebula was excluded from [[Star Wars: The Essential Atlas Online Companion|''The Essential Atlas'' Online Companion]] because it was an imaginary location used as an example.<ref name="Email">{{EmailCite|email=File:EAOC discussion.jpg|creator=Jason Fry|date=2015-06-30}}</ref>

